V1: 24 pages. V2: 25 pages, 2 references added, no physics changes;
  V3: Now 24 Pages; this version closely resembles the final published version.
  (Reformatted; some discussion added; several references added.)

column11:
  For $q>2, \gamma > 1$, we prove that maximal regularity of $L^q$ type holds
for periodic solutions to $-\Delta u + |Du|^\gamma = f$ in $\mathbb{R}^d$,
under the (sharp) assumption $q > d \frac{\gamma-1}\gamma$.
